## 🎨 DESIGN SYSTEM — FRAME OF THAILAND

### Brand Concept
"Frame of Thailand" — Thailand's cinematic stories, framed for the world.
Aesthetic: dark cinematic depth + vibrant Thai creative energy (Official CI colors).
The film strip (◼◼◼◼◼◼) is the visual signature on every section header.
Logo: Official ContentThailand flame "C" icon (gradient orange→pink).

### CSS Design Tokens (Official CI + Frame of Thailand)
```css
/* Backgrounds — CI Midnight Navy */
--midnight:      #14133D;   /* Primary dark bg */
--navy:          #1C1B4E;   /* Card bg */
--navy-hover:    #252466;   /* Card hover */
--surface:       #F8F7F4;   /* Light page bg */
--surface-alt:   #F2F4F7;   /* Alternate rows */

/* Brand — CI Primary */
--purple:        #702874;   /* Royal Purple — accent */
--pink:          #EC1C72;   /* Hot Pink — primary CTA */
--pink-light:    #F43F8A;   /* Hover pink */

/* Brand — CI Secondary */
--orange:        #F76532;   /* Sunset Orange — warm accent */
--amber:         #F6A51B;   /* Amber / Golden Yellow — highlight */

/* Gradients — CI Official */
--gradient-primary:   linear-gradient(135deg, #14133D, #702874, #EC1C72);
--gradient-secondary: linear-gradient(135deg, #F76532, #F6A51B);

/* Text */
--text-primary:  #1A202C;
--text-muted:    #718096;
--text-on-dark:  #F8F7F4;

/* Status */
--success:       #276749;
--error:         #C53030;
--warning:       #C05621;
--info:          #2B6CB0;

/* Borders */
--border:        #E2E8F0;
--border-dark:   #1C1B4E;
```

### Typography (Google Fonts + system)
```
Hero / Display:     "Playfair Display"  — cinematic serif (EN titles)
Thai Headings:      "Sarabun"           — clean Thai weight 600-700
Thai Body:          "Noto Sans Thai"    — readable weight 400
English Body:       "Inter"             — technical clarity
Admin / Data:       "JetBrains Mono"    — IDs, codes, logs
```

### Film Strip Component
Every section title uses FilmStrip decoration:
```tsx
// components/layout/FilmStrip.tsx
// Usage: <FilmStrip><h2>ภาพยนตร์ไทย</h2></FilmStrip>
// Renders: ◼◼◼◼ ภาพยนตร์ไทย ◼◼◼◼
```

### Component Patterns
- **Cards:** `rounded-xl` dark bg, pink border on hover (`border-pink/40`), `shadow-2xl`
- **Badges:** pill shape `rounded-full px-3 py-1`, pink-on-dark or gradient orange→amber
- **Buttons:** Primary = `bg-pink text-white font-bold`, Secondary = `border-pink text-pink`, Accent = `bg-gradient-to-r from-orange to-amber text-midnight`
- **Input:** `bg-navy border-border text-white placeholder:text-muted-foreground`
- **Tables:** Dark striped rows, pink/purple sticky header, sortable with chevron icons
- **Skeleton:** `animate-pulse bg-navy-hover rounded` for all loading states

