## 🛠️ CONFIRMED TECH STACK

| Layer | Technology | Version | Notes |
|-------|-----------|---------|-------|
| Frontend | Next.js App Router | 14.x | TypeScript, RSC, Streaming |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS | 3.x | Custom tokens in tailwind.config |
| UI Kit | shadcn/ui | latest | Radix primitives, dark theme |
| CMS | Strapi | v4.x | Headless REST + GraphQL |
| ORM | Prisma | 5.x | PostgreSQL adapter |
| Database | PostgreSQL | 16 | Docker container |
| Cache | Redis | 7 | Docker container |
| Search | Mock (PoC) → Elasticsearch 8 (prod) | — | Thai ICU analyzer in prod |
| Animation | Framer Motion | 10.x | Page transitions + counters |
| Icons | Lucide React | latest | Consistent icon set |
| Auth (CMS) | Strapi built-in | — | RBAC: SuperAdmin/Editor/Viewer |
| Validation | Zod | 3.x | API + form validation |
| Deploy | Docker Compose | — | VPS → G-Cloud |

