## 📐 DATABASE SCHEMA (Prisma — see DB_SCHEMA.md for full)

Key models: `Film`, `TvSeries`, `Person`, `Company`, `Genre`,
`FilmCrew`, `SeriesCrew`, `Award`, `News`

All models have: `id`, `slug` (unique), `titleTh`, `titleEn`,
`status` (published/draft), `createdAt`, `updatedAt`

