## 🎯 TOR COMPLIANCE MAP

| TOR | กำหนด | Our Implementation |
|-----|-------|-------------------|
| 4.4 | Front End ≥ 11 หน้า | 11 public routes + extras |
| 4.5 | Back End CMS | Strapi v4 + Custom Admin Dashboard |
| 4.6 | Server Thailand + IPv6 + Antivirus + Firewall | Docker → G-Cloud VPS |
| 4.7 | Backup Daily/Weekly/Monthly | `scripts/backup.sh` + cron |
| 4.8 | SEO + Google Analytics | Next.js metadata API + GA4 script |
| 4.9 | Search Menu | SearchBar + /search page + instant results |
| 4.10 | Data Migration | `prisma/seed.ts` + import scripts |
| 4.11 | Data Dictionary + ERD | `docs/ERD.md` auto from Prisma schema |
| 4.13 | Log / Traffic | Morgan + Winston + access log |
| 4.14 | SSL Certificate | Nginx + Let's Encrypt (Certbot) |
| 4.16 | อบรม Admin ≥ 5 คน | `docs/admin-guide.md` + video script |
| 4.17 | PDPA / Cookie Consent | `<CookieBanner>` component |
| 4.19 | รายงานการประชุม | Meeting report template |
| 4.20 | เจ้าหน้าที่ประสานงาน | Contact info in all docs |

> **Code comment convention:** Add `// TOR 4.x` next to every feature
> that directly satisfies a TOR requirement.

