## ⚙️ CODE STANDARDS

### TypeScript
- `"strict": true` always
- No `any` — define interfaces in `types/index.ts`
- Use Zod schemas for all API inputs

### React / Next.js
- Server Components by default
- `"use client"` only for: hooks, events, browser APIs, animations
- `next/image` for all images (with width + height)
- `next/font` for custom fonts (never link in HTML)
- Metadata API for all pages SEO

### Naming
```
Components:   FilmCard.tsx         (PascalCase)
Hooks:        useFilms.ts          (camelCase)
Utils:        formatThaiDate.ts    (camelCase)
Types:        interface Film {}    (PascalCase)
Constants:    MAX_RESULTS = 20     (UPPER_SNAKE)
API routes:   /api/films           (kebab-case)
```

### Thai Language
- Always `titleTh` + `titleEn` for bilingual content
- Thai dates: `dd เดือน พ.ศ. yyyy` format
- Numbers: comma separator `1,254,036`
- Fonts: Sarabun (headings) + Noto Sans Thai (body)

### API Response Shape
```typescript
// All API routes return:
{ data: T, meta: { total, page, limit }, error: null }
// On error:
{ data: null, meta: null, error: { message, code } }
```

