## 🐳 DOCKER COMPOSE SERVICES

```
web       → Next.js    :3000
strapi    → Strapi CMS :1337
postgres  → PostgreSQL :5432
redis     → Redis      :6379
nginx     → Proxy      :80 / :443
```

