## 🚫 NEVER

- Use `npm` or `yarn` — pnpm ONLY
- Use TypeScript `any`
- Skip loading / error states
- Hardcode Thai strings outside mock-data files
- Skip mobile responsive
- Use generic gray placeholder boxes — use aspect-ratio skeleton shimmer
- Commit `.env` files
- Reference AWS services — use G-Cloud or Docker equivalents
- Build outside the current phase scope without asking
- Put readable text inside SVG files that will be scaled down
- Create UI elements smaller than 11px text on screen
